/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"單刀橫傳接波果個前過你都當越位架"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"個人係前面點接波? <br />\n<br />\n2對1 2個人都係晒越位而且2個跟本都係offside位, 家下而且係後傳, 人係越位位無干擾比賽一真都唔會吹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:38:56.000Z","msg":"你呢個情況係前面得返對面龍門 咁你傳果下你隊友要企係後過個波先唔越位 隊友接應前企得前過個波都會計越位"},{"pid":"ff11dd53b23e6ad0d51813049bcda43d68e69a2f","tid":1880420,"uid":9305,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"唔好笑女人唔識越位<br />\n<br />\n呢個post證明左好多球迷都唔識 以為向後傳就唔會越位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c058dbc190985f254ef551de34abd4ab87a949c1","tid":1880420,"uid":199804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f2810ba3d7e9f7d1723976fb24bbb95351028ca","tid":1880420,"uid":33007,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0f8ec801d6ad3e3d72f46959da0f21001b5a3d9d","tid":1880420,"uid":36049,"like":22,"dislike":8,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"0c37b8ccf65277bd55632807427af771897b17e6","tid":1880420,"uid":36359,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T21:40:48.000Z","msg":"個波傳出黎果陣佢係越位位就係越位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔關傳球方向事"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T22:27:43.000Z","msg":"向後傳點越位啊足球大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"向後傳點解唔可以越位啊足球大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"人地講只關球員位置唔關傳球方向事<br />\n佢又問翻人傳球方向<br />\n一個po就釣哂弱智出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e231fe855942239a93dd9ccaf2410ca31975a4d7","tid":1880420,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"屌 真係越位嚟，琴晚未睇就comment咗<br />\n一睇果然係越<br />\n唔識球例唔該摺埋<br />\n<br />\n後傳冇越位嘅情況 係傳球者本身已經喺最前<br />\n接應啫同佢平排or喺佢後面<br />\n<br />\n呢球波 接應者隻後腳喺最前<br />\n所以係越位<br />\n<br />\n屌 比人陰鳩咗添"},{"pid":"5eec4e7db17f8e148712ad69c374f2f75f288338","tid":1880420,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2fc36a8675743e36a1b32bf88a144d7cb759383","tid":1880420,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T20:58:05.000Z","msg":"狼隊慘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n說明越位是足球運動的規則。它對攻方<span style=\"color: red;\">向前傳球</span>時接球運動員允許站到的位置作出嚴格限制。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"A player in an offside position at the moment the ball is played or touched* by a team-mate is only penalised on becoming involved in active play by:<br />\n<br />\n- interfering with play by playing or touching a ball passed or touched by a team-mate or<br />\n<br />\n-  interfering with an opponent by:<br />\n             -  preventing an opponent from playing or being able to play the ball by clearly obstructing the opponent&rsquo;s line of vision or<br />\n<br />\n              -  challenging an opponent for the ball or<br />\n<br />\n                - clearly attempting to play a ball which is close when this action impacts on an opponent or<br />\n<br />\n       -   making an obvious action which clearly impacts on the ability of an opponent to play the ball<br />\n<br />\nor<br />\n<br />\n -gaining an advantage by playing the ball or interfering with an opponent when it has:<br />\n<br />\n        - rebounded or been deflected off the goalpost, crossbar, match official or an opponent<br />\n<br />\n        - been deliberately saved by any opponent"},{"pid":"7d43b51854350f9178dc883edb6660080d20a14b","tid":1880420,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eec4e7db17f8e148712ad69c374f2f75f288338","tid":1880420,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2fc36a8675743e36a1b32bf88a144d7cb759383","tid":1880420,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T20:58:05.000Z","msg":"狼隊慘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n說明越位是足球運動的規則。它對攻方<span style=\"color: red;\">向前傳球</span>時接球運動員允許站到的位置作出嚴格限制。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"A player in an offside position at the moment the ball is played or touched* by a team-mate is only penalised on becoming involved in active play by:<br />\n<br />\n- interfering with play by playing or touching a ball passed or touched by a team-mate or<br />\n<br />\n-  interfering with an opponent by:<br />\n             -  preventing an opponent from playing or being able to play the ball by clearly obstructing the opponent&rsquo;s line of vision or<br />\n<br />\n              -  challenging an opponent for the ball or<br />\n<br />\n                - clearly attempting to play a ball which is close when this action impacts on an opponent or<br />\n<br />\n       -   making an obvious action which clearly impacts on the ability of an opponent to play the ball<br />\n<br />\nor<br />\n<br />\n -gaining an advantage by playing the ball or interfering with an opponent when it has:<br />\n<br />\n        - rebounded or been deflected off the goalpost, crossbar, match official or an opponent<br />\n<br />\n        - been deliberately saved by any opponent"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"邊度講&quot;要個波向前&quot;?"},{"pid":"6d08f9f6cd3a0b6f06349a7934de5dc755554fd2","tid":1880420,"uid":179718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d813d70cfc62241ebb2c2db4cc4b3c897c8ea524","tid":1880420,"uid":29787,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:24:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thefa.com/football-rules-governance/lawsandrules/laws/football-11-11/law-11---offside\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thefa.com%2Ffootball-rules-governance%2Flawsandrules%2Flaws%2Ffootball-11-11%2Flaw-11---offside&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=1788a74b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thefa.com/football-rules-governance/lawsandrules/laws/football-11-11/law-11---offside</a><br />\n<br />\n自己睇，呢球好明顯係offside"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"貼得好，都唔知有咩要爭論<br />\n<br />\n越位係睇攻方球員位置，要同時符合下面3個條件<br />\n(1) 喺守方嗰面半場 + (2)企前過守方排尾 2 嗰個球員+ (3)企得前個波<br />\n已經係越位<br />\n<br />\n所以，已經解釋傳波方向已經唔關事<br />\n只要企喺越位位，後傳都可以越位<br />\n<br />\n另外，有人話單刀橫傳點解唔計越位<br />\n其實都係睇準備接應嗰個喺咩位置<br />\n只要佢喺後過傳俾佢嗰個已經唔計越位<br />\n因為佢一定係後過個波"},{"pid":"f0295db7f33e423658c5c430b69e33c90e826699","tid":1880420,"uid":38461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff11dd53b23e6ad0d51813049bcda43d68e69a2f","tid":1880420,"uid":9305,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"唔好笑女人唔識越位<br />\n<br />\n呢個post證明左好多球迷都唔識 以為向後傳就唔會越位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 仲要大大聲嗰下先柒"},{"pid":"1246be1724bced75a9deddaca4aba7300d1a479d","tid":1880420,"uid":38461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:51:17.000Z","msg":"樓豬去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf7c65f43958b82e13a985cd2b996fe5faf813c","tid":1880420,"uid":39838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"呢球其實即係個球員喺越位位置走返出嚟<br />\n點會唔計越位<br />\n<br />\n樓上有人講2v1單刀橫傳嗰種情況係已經突破咗越位陷阱再橫傳唔會有問題"},{"pid":"8543c5febd996fd306a4578cb74b33090785da29","tid":1880420,"uid":179718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.thefa.com/football-rules-governance/lawsandrules/laws/football-11-11/law-11---offside\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thefa.com%2Ffootball-rules-governance%2Flawsandrules%2Flaws%2Ffootball-11-11%2Flaw-11---offside&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=1788a74b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thefa.com/football-rules-governance/lawsandrules/laws/football-11-11/law-11---offside</a><br />\n<br />\n自己睇，呢球好明顯係offside</blockquote>貼得好，都唔知有咩要爭論<br />\n<br />\n越位係睇攻方球員位置，要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同時符合</span></strong>下面3個條件<br />\n(1) 喺守方嗰面半場 + (2)企前過守方排尾 2 嗰個球員+ (3)企得前<span style=\"color: red;\">過</span>個波<br />\n<br />\n所以，已經解釋傳波方向已經唔關事<br />\n只要本身喺越位位，後傳都可以越位<br />\n<br />\n另外，有人講單刀橫傳點解唔計越位<br />\n其實都係睇準備接應嗰個喺咩位置<br />\n只要佢企喺後過傳俾佢嗰個都好難越位<br />\n因為佢個位置一定<span style=\"color: red;\">後過個波</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f5bccf8f42bd0f95ad8ee70a50a1cfdd0273088d","tid":1880420,"uid":33007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"baf7c65f43958b82e13a985cd2b996fe5faf813c","tid":1880420,"uid":39838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"呢球其實即係個球員喺越位位置走返出嚟<br />\n點會唔計越位<br />\n<br />\n樓上有人講2v1單刀橫傳嗰種情況係已經突破咗越位陷阱再橫傳唔會有問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"你呢個講法都係唔準確，<br />\n假設無攞波跑得前嗰攞波果個，<br />\n攞波果個無論向前定向後傳，<br />\n無攞波果個依然處於越位位置"},{"pid":"445fee9cef42f2a041fb70ecb29cae9a6daa7c5a","tid":1880420,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da88f47332ab5239eebae7254200930e7c1b38bf","tid":1880420,"ui